=== Detailed Description ===


=== Benefit to oVirt ===
Users will be able to add watchdog cards to their virtual machines. This will be especially important for highly available  servers.

=== Dependencies / Related Features ===
This feature depends on the [[Add an option to create a watchdog device|VDSM support for the watchdog cards]] (merged)
The related patch is [http://gerrit.ovirt.org/7535 here]

